data.description: Wonderful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in sought after Arbor Chase Subdivision! Completely remodeled in 2020 including new Architectural Shingle Roof, new HVAC unit, hardwood flooring on main level, granite counters, and many other updates . Main level features family room with fireplace, dining room with open concept to kitchen boasting beautiful granite counter tops, travertine tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and a large island with seating.  Main level also features a nice walk-in pantry, powder room and laundry room.  Additionally, half of the garage has been converted to a large bonus room and the other half remains open for all of your storage needs. Upper level includes the owner's suite boasting a huge walk-in closet and en-suite bath (separate soaking tub and shower, vanity with granite counters).  Additionally, there are three other bedrooms on the upper level; one of which is extra-large with two separate closets! The upper-level hall bath features a tub shower combo and vanity with solid surface counters.  There is also a linen closet for ample storage space. Cozy fenced in back yard. Fresh paint throughout the home and the carpets have been cleaned. *The subdivision has a large community pool, playground, and recreation area. Enjoy easy access, just minutes to local amenities, shopping centers, dining options, and recreational parks. The community also provides a welcoming atmosphere and a sense of belonging.
